
    Hippo_Ajax_Form Class 1.0
    ------------------------------------------------------------------------

    Hippo_Ajax_Form Class provide a easy way to create Ajax Form element,
    and seperate index/PHP/JavaScript in 3 files.
    
    Functions:
    <> supporting Input Text/Select Control/CheckBox/Radio Button/TextArea Controls .
    <> using POST to submit FORMs.
    <> assign specific DIV layer to show PHP execution results.
    <> no more parsing XML, direct outout PHP-HTML codes in DIV Layer.
    <> supporting loading image.
    <> supporting BIG5/Unicode Characters in Ajax output.
    
    There is a workable demo within this package, for more information plz check 'index.php'.

